High There! is the world’s first global social network for cannabis enthusiasts . 
  The app is designed to let users meet friends and form relationships without being judged for their drug use . 
  Users swipe to connect and share their interests and energy levels . 
  When it launched in the US it was only available in states that have legalised cannabis . 
  Now it is available in the Netherlands, Spain and Australia . 
  It can only be downloaded in US and is available on Apple and Google Play . 
  Founder Todd Mitchem said it is the ‘Tinder for marijuana users’ He said the app doesn’t encourage the sale of the drug . 
 